Usage: getLayerPreference [-help] <layer_name> {-isVisible | -isSelectable | -color | -lineWidth | -stipple | -stippleData }

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<layer_name>          # the name of the layer or the object type
                      # (string, required)
-color                # a color name or a numeric RGB value (bool, optional)
-isSelectable         # whether the object is selectable (bool, optional)
-isVisible            # whether the object is visible (bool, optional)
-lineWidth            # number of pixels in the border of the specified object
                      # (bool, optional)
-stipple              # information about the stipple pattern of the object
                      # (bool, optional)
-stippleData          # the stipple information for the object (bool, optional)